HEADWORD: Deflagrator
<hw>Def"la*gra`tor</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>A form of the voltaic battery having large plates, used for
producing rapid and powerful combustion.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

